CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

February 16, 2011

[Cite as 02/1612011 Case Announcements, 2011-Ohio-647.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2010-2118. State ex rel. Buoscio v. Horrigan.

In Mandamus. On complaint in mandamus of Samuel Buoscio. On S.Ct.Prac.R. 10.5 determination, cause dismissed.

O’Connor, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, Cupp, and McGee Brown, JJ., concur.
